{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-11710/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-11710"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:17:10"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Woman helps man exit bathroom"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-11710","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-11710"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1/a60bc851-1ef6-4efb-8df6-49a7e678d033","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:28:39.413Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>When Reynolds leaves the bathroom, he tells Alma it must have been something he ate that made him ill, to which she hums in agreement. The irony is, of course, that she already knows this, having been the one to poison him. When he, unknowingly, calls out the very thing she did, she seems unphased, brushing him off seemingly without any guilt.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:531.3653136531366,147.67527675276745,922.8044280442805,896.2361623616238"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1/d9775942-452a-4a62-b1ff-d0f2e16df116","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:29:00.347Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The Reynolds we see here is a far cry from what we are used to, particularly stark in comparison with the opening scene, which also takes place in his room. His hair is disheveled and falling into his face, his white shirt is drenched, in water or sweat, and he is untying his tie as he walks. While before, the viewers have only seen his bedroom as he is getting ready for his day, here, we see him get un-ready, so to speak, his careful routine entirely undone by Alma’s poisoning.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11710/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:978.5977859778596,101.62361623616228,425.09225092250915,949.3726937269374"}}}]}]}]}